snippet.title: 3D Tennis Android Gameplay
snippet.description:
3D Tennis Android sport game developed by Mouse Games. You can not find tennis players names like Novak Djokovic, Rafael Nadal, Roger Federer, Andy Murray, David Ferrer and other names from ATP list. But you can find players that look lot like them. Controls could be better but all in all ok game.

Google play
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.cg.tennis&hl=en
